description: This file declares the interface functions for the Slap Owo Uoao object, which is part of the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP) component in the broader network service system. It contains function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing the object.

methods.name: SlapCreateOwoUoao
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Owo Uoao object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: SlapOwoUoaoCreate
methods.description: Constructs the Owo Uoao object with given container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: SlapOwoUoaoRemove
methods.description: Removes or deinitializes the Owo Uoao object.

methods.name: SlapOwoUoaoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls or registers internal objects or components within the Owo Uoao object.

methods.name: SlapOwoUoaoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Owo Uoao object, setting up necessary state or configurations.
